        rdfs:comment     "Rationale: Figure 3: Electron micrograph showed Gαi2 (GNAI2) localization in axon terminals of sensory neurons of in the goat olfactory bulb.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Adult female (n=6) and male (n=1) shiba goats (Capra hircus)\"\n\n\"OB sections of the female goats were cut horizontally (10 um thick) and immunostained with mouse anti-Gαi2 (MAB3077)\"" ;
